Setup:

create a .env file in root healthy_meals
since you are running a local db, please use db name, user and password that you have access to.
example:
DB_NAME=dbname
DB_USER=dbuser
DB_PASSWORD=dbpassword
DB_HOST=127.0.0.1
DB_PORT=5432

